<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Souten no Shiroki Kami no Za - Great Peak puts the player in the role of the captain of an expedition of alpinists in this mountain simulation game.
                  <br><br>The game is divided into 2 different parts:
                  <br>1 - The first one is preparing the expedition: Select the team members, make plans for mountain climbling, choose the equipment, select the different routes, camp base, etc
                  <br>2 - The second one is climbimb the mountain: The game features mountain dangers like falling rocks, avalanches, injuries, etc.
                  <br><br>The game features 5 different mountains: K-Zero Niconosa (8955m), Sisha Kanli (8482m), Kanga Purna (8021m), Dhaula Chenli (7686m) & Manutse (7128m).
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Aims to climb the top of the unprecedented scale simulation. Climbing team members to organize the rich individuality, promoting a climbing accident while responding to sudden weather and considering the situation of members, two tough five aims unexplored peaks. Members to put in climbing has grown to become a member dependable, tried to challenge the success of the summit several times.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>First person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Alpinist theme.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

